00:05:05.875 --> 00:05:07.030 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: And attacks the body.

00:05:07.030 --> 00:05:08.238 align:middle line:90%
>>FUCHS: It attacks the body.

00:05:08.238 --> 00:05:10.150 align:middle line:84%
