it in a wrong way.

00:05:10.150 --> 00:05:12.160 align:middle line:84%
It's not crazy and
it's not mistaken.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:14.933 align:middle line:84%
But something has been
distorted in the body.

00:05:14.933 --> 00:05:17.350 align:middle line:84%
When a distortion occurs in a
body-- when we say the body,

00:05:17.350 --> 00:05:18.850 align:middle line:90%
