00:05:26.620 --> 00:05:28.980 align:middle line:84%
It almost always
involves our lifestyle.

00:05:28.980 --> 00:05:30.730 align:middle line:84%
And that's really the
bottom line, George.

00:05:30.730 --> 00:05:34.270 align:middle line:84%
